                <div class="card-body pl-1 pr-1 card-collapse-intro">
                    {!-- ra:0000000059e30c290000000036a60ca9 --}  <h3 class="card-title display chalk-primary">Disaster Management</h3>   <p class="card-text chalk-primary">Rebuilding lives and communities in the aftermath of disasters with smart solutions that empower lives.</p>   <i class="fa fa-plus card-collapse-button" aria-hidden="true"></i> {!-- ra:0000000059e30c280000000036a60ca9 --}
                </div>
                    
                <div class="card-body card-collapse-body hidden">
                    <i class="fa fa-times card-collapse-button" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    <p class="card-text">In any calamity, natural or man-made, it is always the least empowered sections of society that suffer most. At Voltas, we give freely of our time, resources and expertise to help the communities affected. From the Chennai floods of 2004 to the COVID-19 crisis of 2020, we have always been on the front lines, aiding government efforts in containing the damage and rebuilding lives in the aftermath. Also, as part of our continuing effort to improve the lives of AA and tribal communities, we spearheaded a Participatory Groundwater management project for the farmers in Osmanabad. Through our training they learned about effective management of the precious groundwater resources and improving agricultural productivity by using improved agricultural techniques.</p>
