                    {!-- ra:0000000059e30c290000000036a60ca9 --}  <h3 class="card-title display chalk-primary">Water Management & Sanitation</h3>   <p class="card-text chalk-primary">Tackling the biggest crisis in the nation by ensuring the sustainable distribution and usage of water.</p>   <i class="fa fa-plus card-collapse-button" aria-hidden="true"></i> {!-- ra:0000000059e30c280000000036a60ca9 --}
                </div>
                    
                <div class="card-body card-collapse-body hidden">
                    <i class="fa fa-times card-collapse-button" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    <p class="card-text">We have been working to combat the issue of dwindling fresh water resources through education and engineering. By providing rural and tribal communities with the knowledge and resources to create sustainable water management tools, we provide them with the opportunity to focus on other aspects of their development without having to worry about the availability of water. The second aspect of our program has been educating these communities on the importance of having lavatories. As part of the governmentâ€™s Swachh Bharat Initiative we aided communities in numerous locations with access to clean sanitary facilities. We have recently initiated an integrated groundwater management and sustainable agriculture program in the Beed district of Maharashtra. It aims at reducing the impact of drought on 6 villages in the region benefiting the 13,000 people that reside there.</p>
